英軍自韓戰爆發的1950年起加入[[聯合國軍|聯合國軍]]支持[[大韓民國|大韓民國]]一方，在聯軍中是規模僅次於[[美軍|美軍]]的第二大派兵來源。從開戰至1953年《[[朝鮮停戰協定|朝鮮停戰協定]]》簽定為止，英國海陸空三軍共有8萬多名官開赴[[朝鮮半島|朝鮮半島]]前線作戰，當中約1,100多人陣亡<ref name="BBC中文"></ref>。然而在韓戰結束後的英國，對於戰事經過和參戰老兵的關注都相當有限<ref name="BBC中文"></ref>，此種情形到1981年英國韓戰老兵協會（{{lang|en|BKVA}}）創會之後也都沒有消弭<ref name="電訊報">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/history/britain-at-war/11260575/Britains-Korean-War-veterans-win-their-final-fight.html |title=Britain's Korean War veterans win their final fight |author=Joe Shute |publisher=[[每日電訊報|The Telegraph]] |date=2014-11-29 |accessdate=2014-12-22 |archive-date=2019-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191029080031/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/history/britain-at-war/11260575/Britains-Korean-War-veterans-win-their-final-fight.html |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>，甚至常被稱作「被遺忘的戰爭」（{{lang|en|the “forgotten war”}}）<ref name="韓國外交部">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.mofa.go.kr/ENG/press/pressreleases/index.jsp?menu=m_10_20&sp=/webmodule/htsboard/template/read/engreadboard.jsp%3FtypeID=12%26boardid=302%26seqno=314627 |title=16th Korean War Memorial Built on the Bank of the River Thames |publisher=[[大韓民國外交部|ROK Ministry of Foreign Affairs]] |date=2014-12-04 |accessdate=2014-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223054417/http://www.mofa.go.kr/ENG/press/pressreleases/index.jsp?menu=m_10_20&sp=%2Fwebmodule%2Fhtsboard%2Ftemplate%2Fread%2Fengreadboard.jsp%3FtypeID%3D12%26boardid%3D302%26seqno%3D314627 |archive-date=2014-12-23 |dead-url=yes }}}}</ref>。

除此之外，英國在聯合國軍16個參戰國中，也是最晚一個於首都立碑紀念者<ref name="韓國外交部"></ref><ref name="韓國駐英大使館">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author= |url=http://gbr.mofa.go.kr/english/eu/gbr/mission/announcement/index.jsp?sp=/webmodule/htsboard/template/read/engreadboard.jsp%3FtypeID=16%26boardid=9817%26seqno=716018%26tableName=TYPE_ENGLEGATIO |title=The Unveiling of the Korean War Memorial: Remarks by H.E. Yun Byung-se, Minister of Foreign Affairs |publisher={{Link-en|大韓民國駐英國大使館|Embassy of South Korea, London|Embassy of the Republic of Korea in the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland}} |date=2014-12-04 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072452/http://gbr.mofa.go.kr/english/eu/gbr/mission/announcement/index.jsp?sp=%2Fwebmodule%2Fhtsboard%2Ftemplate%2Fread%2Fengreadboard.jsp%3FtypeID%3D16%26boardid%3D9817%26seqno%3D716018%26tableName%3DTYPE_ENGLEGATIO |dead-url=no }}}}</ref><ref name="中央日報">{{zh-hant}}{{cite web|author=高貞愛 |url=http://chinese.joins.com/big5/article.do?method=detail&art_id=128392&category=002002 |title=倫敦也建立韓國-{}-戰爭紀念碑 16個參戰國家都在首都建立 |publisher=[[韓國中央日報|韓國中央日報]] |date=2014-12-05 |accessdate=2014-12-20}}</ref>，在紀念碑造好之前，倫敦境內僅[[聖保羅座堂|聖保羅大教堂]]的地窖掛著韓戰陣亡者銅匾，沒有紀念碑之類的公開式建築，離首都圈最近的紀念地點則位於200公里外、[[史丹佛郡|史丹佛郡]]的{{Link-en|英國國家紀念植物園|National Memorial Arboretum|國家紀念植物園}}內<ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{Citation |format=pdf |url=http://narasarang.mpva.go.kr/hyunchung/overseas625f/user/eng/pdf/eng02.pdf |title=Korean War Memorialsin Pictures: Remembering UN Participation 60 Years Later |publisher=[[大韓民國國家報勳處|ROK Ministry of Patriots and Veterans Affairs]] |date=2010 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |page=pp. 10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202215/http://narasarang.mpva.go.kr/hyunchung/overseas625f/user/eng/pdf/eng02.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}}}</ref>，大部分戰歿英兵的安葬之處更是遠在韓國[[釜山|釜山]]的[[聯合國紀念公墓|聯合國紀念公墓]]<ref name="英國政府"></ref>。

儘管聖保羅大教堂有了紀念牌，英軍韓戰老兵仍繼續呼籲官方增設更大的紀念物<ref name="Joongang1">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author=Sarah Kim |url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2998125 |title=Queen praises Korean War memorial in London |publisher=[[韓國中央日報|Korea Joongang Daily]] |date=2014-12-05 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2019-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622205056/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aId=2998125 |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。1995年時，[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]的[[韓戰老兵紀念碑|韓戰老兵紀念碑]]揭幕啟用，間接成了立碑行動的契機，最後使之在2010年後得以展開<ref name="中央日報"></ref>。韓國方面，其{{Link-en|大韓民國駐英國大使館|Embassy of South Korea, London|駐英大使館}}亦曾數次提出在倫敦立碑的方案，但卻面臨到市區不易獲得用地的問題，向英國文化、環境、國防等[[英國政府部門|中央部門]]及地方政府申請建案批准時也要辦理嚴密的行政手續<ref name="Joongang2">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author=Sarah Kim |url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2975193 |title=World remembers Korean War |publisher=[[韓國中央日報|Korea Joongang Daily]] |date=2013-07-27 |accessdate=2014-12-24 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605005939/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=2975193 |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。

[[File:State_Visit_of_President_Park_Geun-Hye_(10692492663).jpg|thumb]]赴英期間出席紀念碑奠基式，2013年11月5日]]
2012年10月1日{{Link-ko|韓國國軍日|국군의 날}}後，韓國政府透過駐英大使館聯絡了韓裔出身的英國貴族——{{Link-en|李正善，羅瑟米爾子爵夫人|Maiko Jeong Shun Lee, Viscountess Rothermere|羅瑟米爾子爵夫人}}及其下的羅夫人基金會（{{lang|en|Lady R Foundation}}），雙方進而達成合作，由子爵夫人出資5.5萬英鎊作為建設促進費，協助申請立案許可、尋找紀念碑創作人選，韓國政府則予以支援<ref name="Joongang2"></ref>。之後又進行了一年的籌備過程，物色合適的選址、進行碑體設計，並與英國國防部、[[英國外交部|外交部]]及{{Link-en|西敏自治市議會|Westminster City Council}}等英方單位接洽<ref name="Foundation">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.theladyrfoundation.org/index.php/projects/war-memorial/ |title=Korean War Memorial |publisher=The Lady R Foundation |accessdate=2014-12-24 |archive-date=2019-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610200136/http://www.theladyrfoundation.org/index.php/projects/war-memorial/ |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。韓國政府、韓國企業和[[在英韓僑|在英韓僑]]總共為立碑工程捐贈了100萬英鎊<ref name="中央日報"></ref>，除了英國韓戰老兵協會、羅夫人基金會、韓國駐英大使館及英國相關政府部門之外，[[韓國國家報勳處|韓國國家報勳處]]等機構也參與了企劃<ref name="英國政府">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author= |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/memorial-to-the-korean-war-unveiled-in-london |title=Press release: Memorial to the Korean War unveiled in London |publisher=[[英國政府|GOV.UK]] |date=2014-12-03 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207205639/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/memorial-to-the-korean-war-unveiled-in-london |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。

2013年10月，英國政府正式核准了在國防部旁的維多利亞堤岸花園豎立韓戰紀念碑的建案<ref name="Foundation"></ref>。同年11月，[[韓國總統|韓國總統]][[朴槿惠|朴槿惠]]赴英進行[[國事訪問|國事訪問]]，並於到訪期間的11月5日與[[劍橋公爵威廉王子|威廉王子]]一起參加動土儀式、替紀念碑奠基<ref>{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2487821/Britain-lays-pageantry-Queen-welcomes-South-Koreas-female-president.html |title=Prince William continues to take on greater Royal role as he helps the Queen welcome South Korea's first female president |publisher=[[每日郵報|Daily Mail]] |date=2013-11-06 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305070028/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2487821/Britain-lays-pageantry-Queen-welcomes-South-Koreas-female-president.html |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。2014年12月3日下午，韓國駐英大使館替竣工的韓戰紀念碑主辦揭幕典禮，與會者共500人，當中有320名韓戰英軍老兵。到場官員包含英國國防大臣[[邁克爾·法倫|法倫]]、{{Link-en|英國外交國務大臣|Minister of State for Foreign Affairs|外交國務大臣}}[[雨果·施維爾|施維爾]]、韓國駐英大使{{Link-ko|林聖男 (外交官)|임성남 (외교관)|林聖男}}、英國駐韓大使魏特曼（{{lang|en|Scott Wightman}}）<ref name="在英韓僑">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author=Warwick Morris |url=http://www.britishkoreansociety.org.uk/news/memorial-to-britains-role-in-the-korean-war-unveiled-in-london/ |title=Memorial to Britain’s role in the Korean War unveiled in London |publisher=British Korean Society |date=2014-12-08 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930191806/http://www.britishkoreansociety.org.uk/news/memorial-to-britains-role-in-the-korean-war-unveiled-in-london/ |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>及[[韓國陸軍|韓國陸軍]]參謀總長[[金曜煥|金曜煥]]上將<ref name="韓國外交部"></ref>等人，[[理查親王_(格洛斯特公爵)|格洛斯特公爵]]和[[韓國外交部|韓國外交部長]][[尹炳世|尹炳世]]則分別代表[[英國女王|英國女王]][[伊麗莎白二世|伊麗莎白二世]]和朴槿惠總統出席<ref name="在英韓僑"></ref><ref name="英國政府"></ref>。格洛斯特公爵在會場上代讀了伊麗莎白女王的賀詞，當中稱韓戰紀念碑是「大韓民國人民和政府慷慨捐贈的禮物」{{efn|原文：「{{lang|en|kindly gifted by the people and government of the Republic of Korea.}}」<ref name="女王"></ref>|name="發言1"}}、並「將恆久昭示[[韓英關係|兩國間的堅強友誼]]」{{efn|原文：「{{lang|en|it will be an enduring reminder of the strong friendship that exists between our two countries.}}」<ref name="女王"></ref>|name="發言2"}}<ref name="女王">{{en}}{{lang|en|{{cite web |author= |url=http://gbr.mofa.go.kr/english/eu/gbr/mission/announcement/index.jsp?sp=/webmodule/htsboard/template/read/engreadboard.jsp%3FtypeID=16%26boardid=9817%26seqno=716029%26tableName=TYPE_ENGLEGATIO |title=The Unveiling of the Korean War Memorial: A message from H.M. Queen, Elizabeth II |publisher={{Link-en|大韓民國駐英國大使館|Embassy of South Korea, London|Embassy of the Republic of Korea in the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland}} |date=2014-12-04 |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100215/http://gbr.mofa.go.kr/english/eu/gbr/mission/announcement/index.jsp?sp=%2Fwebmodule%2Fhtsboard%2Ftemplate%2Fread%2Fengreadboard.jsp%3FtypeID%3D16%26boardid%3D9817%26seqno%3D716029%26tableName%3DTYPE_ENGLEGATIO |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。

